  "body": "# Problem\r\n\r\nWhen pressing sign out, the user can sometime briefly see a profile screen with \"Unknown\" as name.\r\n\r\n## Implementation\r\n\r\nThis is due to the fact that all user data is flushed on sign out but for a moment the profile screen is still visible.\r\nA spinning wheel similar to what is shown on account creation and login should be shown instead.\r\n\r\n## Acceptance Criteria\r\n\r\nUser never sees \"Unknown\" profile",
